text: Anaespogonius piceonigris is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hayashi in 1972. It is known from Japan.BioLib.cz - Anaespogonius piceonigris. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1972
